(ooc: element was actually firing at jp's troops, but that's ok :)

Element turned when several blasts hit his armor and made dents in it. He 
was a big big gestalt though so it didn't do any real damage. Element fires 
two missiles at Tantrum and mentally guided them to their target while 
running at Tantrum and trying to squash him with his large foot.


Cyndro continued to fire at Hell Beast and his troups. He wasn't going to go 
easy on them (JP, Cyndro is firing EMP blasts and missiles and everything, 
so post for them too. they'd probably hit because Hell Beast is so close and 
Cyndro is a deadly aim). The disk on top of the Element (ship) fired another 
shockwave at Hell Beast. This one was even stronger than the last, and was 
almost bound to knock some bots down.





The Maximal ship flew down toward earth, but escape pods were already 
launching off. Five in all, the pods had a Maximal symbol on it, as well as 
a bunch of emergency equipment (the scanner thingies :). The ship crashed 
and exploded several dozen miles away from the Cybertronian Fire, and the 
pods landed in a mile radius around it. The pods began to scan for nice 
lifeforms to use on this planet.
